octeon_recv_pkt_t Struct Reference

#include <cavium_kernel_defs.h>

Detailed Description

Receive Packet format used when dispatching output queue packets with non-raw opcodes.

The received packet will be sent to the upper layers using this structure which is passed as a parameter to the dispatch function
